ttp_template:
<group name="action_description_ge_le">
Prefix-list: {{PREFIX_LIST | ORPHRASE}}
Description: {{DESCRIPTION | ORPHRASE}}
Seq: {{SEQUENCE}}, {{ACTION}}: {{PREFIX | ORPHRASE}}
  ge {{GE}} le {{LE | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Prefix-list: PL-TEST
Description: Sample Prefix-list for demonstration
Seq: 5, Permit: 192.168.10.0/24
  Match conditions:
    ge 25 le 30
Seq: 10, Deny: 10.0.0.0/8
Seq: 15, Permit: 172.16.0.0/12

Total no of prefixes: 3
textfsm_template:
Value PREFIX_LIST (\S+)
Value DESCRIPTION (.*)
Value SEQUENCE (\d+)
Value ACTION (\S+)
Value PREFIX (\S+/\d+)
Value GE (\d+)
Value LE (\d+)

Start
  ^Prefix-list:\s+${PREFIX_LIST}
  ^Description:\s+${DESCRIPTION}
  ^Seq:\s+${SEQUENCE},\s+${ACTION}:\s+${PREFIX}
  ^\s*Match conditions:\s*$$
  ^\s*ge\s+${GE}\s+le\s+${LE} -> Record
  ^Seq:\s+${SEQUENCE},\s+${ACTION}:\s+${PREFIX} -> Record

EOF
